@page "/"

<PageTitle>Brand Voice Consistency Checker</PageTitle>

<div class="container-fluid mt-4">
    <div class="row mb-4">
        <div class="col-12 text-center">
            <h2 class="display-5">Brand Voice Consistency Checker</h2>
            <p class="text-muted">
                Paste your marketing copy and brand guidelines to receive a structured consistency
                report with severity scores, category-level violations, and targeted rewrite suggestions
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-12">
            <BrandCheckerWidget />
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row mt-5">
        <div class="col-12">
            <div class="alert alert-info" role="alert">
                <h5 class="alert-heading"><i class="bi bi-info-circle me-2"></i>About This Demo</h5>
                <p class="mb-0">
                    This pipeline runs three sequential stages: <strong>semantic embedding</strong> — both the copy
                    and brand guidelines are embedded to compute a cosine similarity score that quantifies semantic drift;
                    <strong>deviation analysis</strong> — an LLM identifies specific tone, vocabulary, formality, and
                    style violations against the guidelines; and <strong>rewrite generation</strong> — a dedicated LLM
                    call produces drop-in corrections for each flagged excerpt. Each stage has a clear responsibility,
                    making the report auditable and independently reviewable.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
